         <abstract id="aspace_36688970cab26319d5819d5a287f7b76">The materials consist of stereographs of Yale and New Haven, Connecticut from the late 19th century. The majority depict buildings, street scenes, views of the New Haven Green, East Rock Park, West Rock, and Fair Haven.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_91041fdcb6bcf5a8400eefa547f07308">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 48-A (YRG 48-A), Yale pictorial records and collections.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_9a93744df5c3f9f3664effd57d697aeb">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Yale and New Haven Stereograph Collection (RU 689). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_bac394a7e4a2962b2d2c2fce11eea3cf">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_4f62ae0d8cc58e14cea6e3f6c327952b">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by subject.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_de0bbc5e8901c80f438642bac3839c7d">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of stereographs of Yale and New Haven, Connecticut from the late 19th century. The majority depict buildings, street scenes, views of the New Haven Green, East Rock Park, West Rock, and Fair Haven.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
